Name: Irene
Description:
Irene's body was found in her home with multiple stab wounds.

Note that we do not know the exact date of her death - only that it took place in July 2005.

> Irene was a 44 year old transsexual [woman], originally from Thailand. Her body was discovered at her home, where she had been stabbed several times and bled to death.
